                            <comment id="63767" author="spimpale" created="Wed, 7 Aug 2013 12:18:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The introduction of lmm_layout_gen in lov_mds_md_v1 makes the assumption that lmm_objects is present after lmm_stripe_count incorrect.&lt;br/&gt;
